{
  "stem": "13251.4",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 436.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Cleveland, yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And in New York [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I guess my aunt thought I was going to be like an adopted child because they didn't have any children.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Her husband had lost his family in the war.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "She had lost a child.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And this was a, a late marriage.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They got married, I think, in Cleveland [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] shortly before that.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And then they, they moved to New York and opened up a business, you know, a luncheonette, and they were doing quite well.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They worked hard, though.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I have to give them credit.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I just wasn't comfortable being an adopted child at the age of 25.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I started going out and then meeting people.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And, and they didn't like that.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And there was friction building up and stuff.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I-- in fact, while I was there, they kept telling me that America was a rough country.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You have to work, work hard.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And when they came, they worked for dollar an hour and all that in factories and God knows what, you know, sewing like most immigrants did from Europe.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I came to United States.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I knew the language.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I had a good profession, and I found a job very easily.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I made a few calls.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I figured, I don't know my way around.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So I called an agency, an employment agency, found me a job almost instantly.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "My first job was NYU at the university in the printing department as a cameraman.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It was the easiest job I ever had in my life.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And that's how I came to America to work hard.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They don't pay much, but it was a great job.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Good environment, friendly and everything.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, fine.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Fine.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, no, no.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
